---
import "../styles/global.css";
import "../styles/about.css";

import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import AboutTabs from "../components/AboutTabs.tsx";
---

<BaseLayout mainHeading="About" pageIndex="iii">
  <!-- ── Intro ──────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <div class="about-intro">
    <div class="about-intro__bio">
      <p>
        Hi I'm Cassi. I'm a frontend engineer focused on web development and web
        engineering.
      </p>
      <p>
        I started out as a Visual Journalism major focusing on photography and
        design, and have worn many hats since then from customer service to
        email development.
      </p>

      <p>
        I eventually made the shift to web development as it's something I've
        always enjoyed doing. I specialize in CMS-based web development and
        enjoy the challenge of empowering content editors to not really need me
        anymore. I'm skilled at ramping up on any CMS but I've spent the most
        time in the world of Contentful, Wordpress and most recently, Shopify.
        I'm also skilled in the world of modern web development, specializing in
        React.js.
      </p>
      <p>
        I know it's a cliche to say that you thrive at the intersection of
        something, but LinkedIn jargon aside, my diverse background really does
        mean that I enjoy and thrive at solving problems that bridge the gap
        between design, development, marketing, and user experience.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of work I like to spend a lot of time outdoors, getting crafty
        with some knitting or illustration, or playing a cozy video game. You
        can see what craft project I'm working on over at my studio or see what
        I'm up to in general now.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-intro__photo">
      <!-- Replace src with your actual photo path -->
      <!-- <img src="/your-photo.jpg" alt="Cassi Gallagher-Shearer" /> -->
      <div class="about-intro__photo--placeholder">photo</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── Tabbed Detail Section ──────────────────────────── -->
  <AboutTabs client:load />
</BaseLayout>
